text.section:
Any offense defined outside this code for which a law outside this code provides a sentence to a term of imprisonment in the state for:
At least one (1) but not more than five (5) years shall be deemed a Class D felony;
At least five (5) but not more than ten (10) years shall be deemed a Class C felony;
At least ten (10) but not more than twenty (20) years shall be deemed a Class B felony;
For at least twenty (20) but not more than fifty (50) years or for life shall be deemed a Class A felony.
